## Design System

### Sandy Serenity Palette

| Color Name | Hex | Usage |
|------------|-----|-------|
| Cream Light | `#f1e6b2` | Backgrounds, chips |
| Gold Sand | `#e2c68a` | Borders, secondary text |
| Di Serria | `#d4a54e` | USSD text, dark accent |
| Marigold | `#c48f2b` | Primary accent |
| Copper | `#a8752f` | Labels, tertiary text |
| Dallas | `#7a5d2c` | Muted text |
| Judge Gray | `#4f3f2e` | Dark surfaces, dividers |
| Thunder | `#2e292b` | Body text |

### Dark Mode

All components support a full dark mode with a black background and warm brown accents.

